    "description": "<p>Paladins devote their life to a cause and fight with empowered righteous fury. They emit an aura to protect those who stand with them... and wield weapons with divine power to smite down those who stand against them.</p><p><strong>Source of Power:</strong> Paladins gain their power from their belief and devotion to their cause. A Paladin that grew up in a small forest and fights to protect the last oak tree could gain magical powers from his passion to protect it. A Paladin whose loved ones were slain could gain powers from his hatred and desire for vengeance toward the perpetrators.</p><p> </p><h2>Starting Equipment</h2><ul><li>2 Light Weapons, or Heavy Weapons or Shields</li><li>1 Ranged Weapon with 20 Ammo OR 3 Throwing Weapons</li><li>1 set of Novice Light or Heavy Armor</li><li>X or Y “Packs” (Adventuring Packs Coming Soon)</li></ul><p> </p><h2>Paladin Martial Mastery</h2><p><strong>Combat Masteries: </strong>All Weapons, All Armors, and All Shields. </p><p><span style=\"font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Weapon Passives:</strong> You gain access to all Weapon Style Passives.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin: 0.5em 0px; color: rgb(25, 24, 19); font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: start\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Maneuvers:</strong> You learn all Attack & Weapon Maneuvers plus additional Maneuvers as shown in the Maneuvers Known column of the Class Table.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin: 0.5em 0px; color: rgb(25, 24, 19); font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: start\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Techniques:</strong> You learn a number of Techniques as shown in the Techniques Known column of the Class Table.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin: 0.5em 0px; color: rgb(25, 24, 19); font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: start\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Stamina Points:</strong> You have a maximum number of Stamina Points as shown in the Stamina Points column of the Class Table.</span></p><p> </p><h2>Paladin Spellcasting Mastery</h2><p><strong>Combat Masteries: </strong>Spellcasting.</p><p><strong>Spell List:</strong> When you learn a new Spell, you can choose any Spell on the Divine Spell List, but only Spells from the following Schools of Magic: Abjuration, Conjuration, Divination, Enchantment, and Transmutation.</p><p><strong>Alpha Note:</strong> You get access to the “Premade List” of “Holy Restoration” and can only choose Spells from that list that are from the above Spell Schools.</p><p><span style=\"font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Cantrips Known: </strong>You learn a number of Spells with the Cantrip Spell Tag as shown in the Cantrips Known column of the Class Table.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin: 0.5em 0px; color: rgb(25, 24, 19); font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: start\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Spells Known:</strong> You learn an additional number of Spells (with or without the Cantrip Spell Tag) as shown in the Spells Known column of the Class Table.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin: 0.5em 0px; color: rgb(25, 24, 19); font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-s